name: Exculpate the Blaster
effect:
[AUTO](VC):When placed, [COST][Counter-Blast 1], choose one card from your soul, put all of the other cards from your soul into the drop zone, and when this unit attacks during this turn, this unit battles all of your opponent's units in one attack.
[AUTO](VC):At the end of the battle that it attacked, put two cards from your hand into your soul, retire this unit, and ride a "Blaster Blade" from your soul as [Stand]. If you could not ride, you lose.

name: Transcendence Dragon, Dragonic Nouvelle Vague
effect: [ACT](VC)[1/turn]:[COST][Soul-Blast 1] grade 3 or greater], and until end of turn, all of your opponent's trigger effects are nullified, and this unit gets [Power] +20000/drive -1. If you or your opponent has five cards in the damage zone, retire all of your opponent's rear-guards.

name: Sage of Salvation, Benon
effect: [AUTO](RC):When placed, [COST][reveal an "Exculpate the Blaster" from your hand, and return it to your deck], search your deck for up to one "Alfred Early", reveal it, put it into your hand, and shuffle your deck.

name: Sage of Guidance, Zenon
effect: [AUTO](RC):When placed from hand, you may reveal the top card of your deck. If that card's grade is the same as your vanguard, ride that card as [Stand], and if not, put it into the drop zone.

name: Nouvellecritic Dragon
effect: [AUTO](RC):When its attack hits a vanguard, search your deck for up to one "Transcendence Dragon, Dragonic Nouvelle Vague", reveal it, put it into your hand, and shuffle your deck.

name: Nouvelleroman Dragon
effect: [AUTO](RC):When placed, [COST][reveal a "Transcendence Dragon, Dragonic Nouvelle Vague" from your hand, and return it to your deck], search your deck for up to one "Dragonic Overlord", reveal it, put it into your hand, and shuffle your deck.

name: Alfred Early
effect: [AUTO](VC):When placed, [COST][Counter-Blast 1], call up to one "Blaster Blade" from your hand or soul to (RC), and that unit gets [Power] +10000 until end of turn. If you called, draw a card.

name: Blaster Blade
effect:
[CONT](VC):If you have four or more rear-guards, this unit gets [Critical] +1.
[AUTO](VC/RC):When placed, [COST][Counter-Blast 1 & Soul-Blast 1], choose one of your opponent's rear-guards in the front row, and retire it.
